@Merchant.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005

### Create Merchant
POST {{Merchant.Api_HostAddress}}/merchant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Merchant",
  "description": "A sample merchant",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City, State",
  "phoneNumber": "555-1234",
  "email": "merchant@example.com"
}

###

### Get Merchant by ID
GET {{Merchant.Api_HostAddress}}/merchant/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Merchant
PUT {{Merchant.Api_HostAddress}}/merchant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "Updated Merchant",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "address": "456 Updated Street, City, State",
  "phoneNumber": "555-5678",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete Merchant
DELETE {{Merchant.Api_HostAddress}}/merchant/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###
